*'''''switch_User_ToolbarIconSize'''''
** if = {{FALSE}}: the icon toolBar respect the FreeCAD value for the icon size
** if = {{TRUE}}: the icon take the values of the variable '''seT_User_sizeIconX''' and '''seT_User_sizeIconY'''
